data.description: NEW LOWER PRICE! Have you ever said I'd like to have a nice home, on an acre of land, close to town, with a gorgeous view - without breaking the bank?  Here is your opportunity.  This home offers a modern open concept with spacious kitchen, vaulted great room leading to new deck, large main bathroom with linen closet, master bedroom with half bath, plus 2nd bedroom, main floor laundry, enclosed bonus room (could be family room, 3rd bedroom, office, etc), 2 car garage, all on acre of ground with easy care vinyl siding, newer roof, and full basement. List of new items: 2012- New furnace, new subfloor, carpet, vinyl, throughout home, new stairwell guardwall; 2013-removed old roof & replaced sheathing and shingles (30 year shingles), new windows and exterior doors; 2014- new water heater, new siding, replaced studs, wiring, lighting, carpet & drywall in bonus room plus added sidewalk from bonus room to deck; 2015-new carpet in NW bedroom, paint, new south deck 12 x 24 and north deck 6 x 14
